      type             : AUDIT_XML
      description      : "1.2.2 Ensure 'Permitted IP Addresses' is set for all management profiles where SSH, HTTPS, or SNMP is enabled  - SSH"
      info             : "For all management profiles, only the IP addresses required for device management should be specified.
